function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	if  not Hydra.IsPlayerVariableSet(idActor, "PrologueHeardLorathBark") then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convLorathChoiceBark,idActor, actorLorath)
		Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idActor, "PrologueHeardLorathBark")
	end
end

function Start(idActorVendor, idItem, idActorPlayer)

	Hydra.SetGameVariableFlag("ProloguePlayerHasLorathsPolearm", true)
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convFenceGivesAmulet, actorMerchant)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorAmulet)
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorLorath)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorHorse)
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
--[[
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convFenceGivesAmulet, actorMerchant)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorAmulet)
--]]
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	Hydra.ItemGiveQuestItemToPlayer(idActorPlayer, itemAmulet, "QST_Prologue_Kyovashad_01")
	Hydra.SetGameVariableFlag("ProloguePlayerHasLorathsAmulet", true)

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convLorathHorse, actorLorath, actorHorseTrader)
	Hydra.QActorFaceActor(actorHorseTrader, actorLorath)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(actorHorseTrader, convLorathHorse)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorHorseTrader, actorHorseTraderFacing)
end
